sentences.english: Leadership Don't get blinded by the cult-hero worshiped "Big L" leaders;
sentences.chinese: 领导能力无须盲目崇拜“大人物”领导者。

sentences.english: Any purchase of a little potassium permanganate for individual self-use need not be put on archives.
sentences.chinese: 个人自用购买少量高锰酸钾的，无须备案。

sentences.english: Residents of the U. S. do not need to take iodine pills to prevent radiation-induced thyroid cancer.
sentences.chinese: 美国居民无须服用碘片来预防辐射造成的甲状腺癌症。

sentences.english: Ben jonson tells us that shakespeare never had to revise a manuscript.
sentences.chinese: 本琼森告诉我们莎士比亚从来无须订正手稿。

sentences.english: The legislative intent of the Basic Law was clear and there was no need for an interpretation.
sentences.chinese: 基本法的立法原意明确，故无须释法。

sentences.english: Employees don't have your typical 9-to-5 schedule.
sentences.chinese: 员工无须遵从典型的朝9晚5工作制。

sentences.english: Simple and practical, green software, no need to install.
sentences.chinese: 简洁实用，绿色软件，无须安装。

sentences.english: For remote-workbench debugging, you won't need to specify a project.
sentences.chinese: 对于远程工作台调试，您无须指定项目。

sentences.english: The struggle, if there were one, need not be described.
sentences.chinese: 如果这算是一场激争，那是无须描述的。

sentences.english: Photography, of course, was eaten by software long ago.
sentences.chinese: 摄影，更无须说，很久以前就已被软件所吞噬。

sentences.english: Elements on your page do not have to be confined to individual grid units. In a five-column grid, 5 narrow columns of text can be hard to read.
sentences.chinese: 你无须强制你页面上的元素都限制于单个单元格。

sentences.english: To do this they had no need to break with Bolshevism.
sentences.chinese: 为了这样做他们无须和布尔什维克主义决裂。

sentences.english: Shareholdings held by a Member's spouse and infant children are not registrable.
sentences.chinese: 委员的配偶及未成年子女所持有的股份无须登记。

sentences.english: Life without over a hundred years, health on the line.
sentences.chinese: 生命无须过百岁，健康就行。

sentences.english: Anything you know you know you can leave out of your notes.
sentences.chinese: 任可你认为你知道都无须出现在笔记上。

sentences.english: He says this is the first time he hasn't had to submit a film to the test-screening process (although there have been screenings for marketing purposes).
sentences.chinese: 他说这是他第一次无须将影片交去试映。

definition: need not/does not have to/not necessarily
solely engrossed in one thing/just (one thing, no need to worry about the rest)/simply/by all means/please feel free/do not hesitate (to ask for sth)
to save/to get rid of (so saving space)
to take a lot of trouble (over sb or sth)/may I trouble you (to do sth)
to have no right/to have no authority
to spend effort/to take trouble/May I trouble you to...? (as part of polite request)/Please would you mind...?
